 "title": "Revelations to Antoine Dareus",
 "summary": "Disguised in false facial hair, hair dye, and his trademark black fedora, the Admiral Danik Kreldin slips into a bar on the hunt for an Imperial Ambassador, just as he was a month before. Nearby, the spice-using pilot Axel basks in the attentions of two local girls while warily watching for bounty hunters, and the Sarian Asli brushes past. Posing as simple Corellian nobility on Imperial business, the figure trades veiled courtesies with Kiare, who reveals her own Corellian noble lineage. The tense, deception-laden encounter sets revelations in motion around Antoine Dareus and the players circling him.",
